title: Trailer home fire in South Sioux City under investigation 17 hours ago
content: Trailer home fire in South Sioux City under investigation    SIOUX CITY, Ia —    Fire crews were working Friday night to extinguish a fire at a trailer in the Siouxland Estates mobile home park near Atokad Park.    That fire broke out just after 7:00 PM Friday night and by the time firefighters arrived that unit was fully engulfed with flames.    Fortunately, the owner of the trailer was not home at the time.    Firefighters tell us the cause of the fire is still under investigation, but it did significant damage to that trailer.
